# Repository Naming Convention

## Format
```
[project_name]-[organization_name]-[type]
```

## Rules
- `project_name`: use `_` to connect words within the name
- `organization_name`: organization or team name (lowercase)
- `type`: `study`, `project`, `research`, `course`, `competition` etc.
- All lowercase, use `-` between segments

## Examples
```
price_prediction-dacon-competition   ✅
youtube_age_analysis-dscover-research ✅
data_structure-skku-course           ✅
python_crawling-personal-study       ✅

price-prediction-dacon-competition   ❌ (spaces in project_name should use _)
```
